{"tid":1838401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭 : 對示威者訴求絕不讓步","createTime":"2020-01-24T04:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T04:18:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"acab02e7c17b46c16a4f4a511400ad84ba281d59","tid":1838401,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥在瑞士達沃斯參與青年主席組織舉辦研討會時，提及香港近期局勢。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥稱，維護《基本法》賦予的權利和自由、維護香港法治同樣重要，不幸地，香港警隊備受誤解，最近受到很多攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n她又批評示威活動有暴力升級趨勢，強調面對示威者提出的政治訴求，須堅持多個重要原則，並清楚表明絕不讓步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2362289/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%3A%E5%B0%8D%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82%E7%B5%95%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%93%E6%AD%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2362289%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%253A%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%25B5%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%25AD%25A5&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=18dd7640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2362289/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%3A%E5%B0%8D%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82%E7%B5%95%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%93%E6%AD%A5</a>"},{"pid":"f669824b33cfbab09b6ea250a0aa483a0646ffcb","tid":1838401,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:14:30.000Z","msg":"呢隻黑警私家雞真係夠哂忠心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b582bbb471431d187270186d47321d9169cb4c","tid":1838401,"uid":265291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:14:32.000Z","msg":"一早知佢唔係冇回應5大訴求, 佢係回應咗唔肯<br />\n所以應該唔係叫佢回應5大訴求, 係叫佢答應"},{"pid":"3f0a67fa5552676937bd7c695e0dfd7049cc0c25","tid":1838401,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:15:00.000Z","